            "en": "Strong CP generation and teamwide {B/BT_ACTION_GAUGE}.",
            "jp": "強力なCP生成と全体{B/BT_ACTION_GAUGE}。",
            "kr": "강력한 CP 생성과 전체 {B/BT_ACTION_GAUGE}.",
